{"tid":2488413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經post 畫樹]  入嚟放低棵樹, 我話你知你係一個點嘅人","createTime":"2021-04-14T08:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T11:37:20.000Z","uid":62752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e7291a1ff0e2fae3d7de175d5abab83c6600f9af","tid":2488413,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"一年一度畫樹又嚟啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果各位巴絲有興趣透過畫畫了解自己的性格，可以根據以下的指示進行心理測驗：<br />\n<br />\n1. 預備一張白紙，一盒/多盒不同種類的顏色筆<br />\n2. 在舒服的環境下繪畫<br />\n3. 在紙上畫出一棵樹<br />\n4. 形狀大小、樹葉、樹幹、果實隨你喜歡<br />\n5. 幫棵樹諗三個形容詞 (可以寫係畫上/post)<br />\n<br />\n利申：有上過堂，純粹與巴絲作簡單的性格分析，內容只供參考！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲唔想公開討論，亦可透過以下方法傳送照片<br />\nSignal / Whatsapp : 9377 3666<br />\nTelegram : <a href=\"https://t.me/caritasinfinityteens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcaritasinfinityteens&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzviC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=f6b5522f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/caritasinfinityteens</a><br />\n<br />\n為左可以更專注咁回覆大家嘅畫，<br />\n我會逢星期三，六 好專心同努力咁覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018POST: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/426501/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/426501/page/1</a><br />\n2019POST: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1044697/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1044697/page/1</a><br />\n2020POST: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1982159/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1982159/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2165fe36a2e215d960f49802d595c6fe96d1d3f1","tid":2488413,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"了解完性格 跟住點？"},{"pid":"8d1b92bf60b22e78c14a85c6cce19d2ef9da1ff4","tid":2488413,"uid":246299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20